OL,3,CForty containers that fell off three
OL,4,Cvessels now recovered or sunk, says MCA
OL,6,FMost of the containers swept overboard
OL,7,Foff the south coast have now either
OL,8,Fbeen recovered or believed to have
OL,9,Fsunk, the Maritime and Coastguard
OL,10,FAgency (MCA) have revealed.
OL,12,FA total of 40 shipping containers have
OL,13,Ffallen from three vessels over the
OL,14,Flast two months.
OL,16,FThe MCA said 17 containers were
OL,17,Freported falling into the sea from a
OL,18,Fcargo ship near Nab Tower at 11.10pm
OL,19,Fon Thursday (8 January) during Storm
OL,20,FGoretti.
