OL,3,CForty containers that fell off three
OL,4,Cvessels now recovered or sunk, says MCA
OL,6,FSeven empty containers are then
OL,7,Freported to have fallen from a second
OL,8,Fship which was 16 nautical miles south
OL,9,Fof St Catherine's Point, Isle of
OL,10,FWight, at 11.55pm.
OL,12,FIt follows a similar incident in
OL,13,FDecember that saw 16 containers,
OL,14,Fcarrying mainly bananas, had fallen
OL,15,Foff the cargo ship Baltic Klipper near
OL,16,Fthe Nab tower lighthouse off Bembridge
OL,17,Fat about 6pm on Saturday (6 December).
