OL,3,CForty containers that fell off three
OL,4,Cvessels now recovered or sunk, says MCA
OL,6,FWhole containers, fragments of metal,
OL,7,Fand food including bananas, avocados,
OL,8,Funcooked chips and onions, have since
OL,9,Fwashed up at various coastal locations
OL,10,Fin Hampshire, Sussex and Kent.
OL,12,FThe MCA said it estimates that most of
OL,13,Fthe containers have now been recovered
OL,14,For are believed to have sunk
OL,15,F"relatively close to the point of
OL,16,Floss".
OL,18,FAn aircraft has been surveilling
OL,19,Fwaters off the Isle of Wight, East
OL,20,FHampshire and East and West Sussex
OL,21,Fsince the incidents took place.
