OL,3,CForty containers that fell off three
OL,4,Cvessels now recovered or sunk, says MCA
OL,6,FThe MCA said fragments of containers
OL,7,Fhave been recovered from the sea and
OL,8,Ftaken ashore to be disposed.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the MCA said: "HM
OL,11,FCoastguard has broadcast navigational
OL,12,Fwarnings in the affected areas.
OL,14,F"Mariners should always keep a proper
OL,15,Flookout while at sea and report
OL,16,Fhazards to HM Coastguard.
OL,18,F"The vessels' owners are responsible
OL,19,Ffor recovering the containers, which
OL,20,Fis being managed through a tactical
OL,21,Fcoordination group of stakeholders.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
