OL,3,CForty containers that fell off three
OL,4,Cvessels now recovered or sunk, says MCA
OL,6,F"HM Coastguard has closely monitored
OL,7,Fthe situation, liaising with the
OL,8,Foperators, salvors, local authorities
OL,9,Fand other organisations.
OL,11,F"The three vessels all made timely
OL,12,Freports of their cargo loss to HM
OL,13,FCoastguard, as required under
OL,14,FInternational Maritime Organization
OL,15,Fconvention.
OL,17,F"The MCA will always assess suspected
OL,18,Fsignificant breaches of maritime
OL,19,Fregulations."
